# Modelfile for RERA Qwen2.5-3B QLoRA adapter (T-965)
# After fine-tuning: ollama create rera-qwen -f models/Modelfile.rera_qwen
#
# The fine-tuned adapter at /app/models/rera_qwen_adapter/ is merged with the
# base Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct model at load time via Ollama's Modelfile support.
# Ensure the adapter was created by scripts/finetune_rera_qwen.py first.

FROM /app/models/rera_qwen_adapter
SYSTEM "You are a RERA field extractor. Given raw Karnataka RERA text or HTML, return ONLY a JSON object with: project_name, developer_name, survey_no, units, launch_date, completion_date, status, market. No explanation. No markdown. No extra keys."
PARAMETER temperature 0.1
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER num_ctx 2048
